tags.note: Open exclusively to residents of the Manhasset Bay Park District. The park is located on the former site of the Port Washington UFSD's Merriman School. Named for former Main Street School principal Charlotte Merriman (as was the school).

tags.description: Named for former Flower Hill resident and Trustee (and eventually Village Engineer) Charles F. Vachris. Vachris donated the services for the construction of this basketball court, and the Village of Flower Hill named the court in his honor.
